      .content
        div.container
          .row.start-md
            .col-md-4
              h2.text-subtitle.text-blue.reveal.effect.effect-reveal Looking ahead to 2018, the industry sees opportunity in cross-device and programmatic campaigns.
              .strip.blue
              .spacer
              .text-body.effect.effect-reveal
                p.text-blue When asked about greater opportunities in 2018, the industry is putting its chips on cross-device and programmatic solutions. Over half of respondents see cross device campaigns, programmatic TV, and programmatic advertising as greater opportunities compared to 2017.
              .foot-note.blue.effect.effect-fadeIn
                img.foot-note__icon(src="images/question-red.svg")
                p.text-blue In your opinion, which of the following industry challenges do you see becoming an opportunity in 2018 compared to 2017? (Please select all that apply).
            .col-md-8
              h4.chart__title.text-blue.effect.effect-reveal
                  | Top industry opportunities in 2018
                  br
                  | (% total respondents)
              video.chart.effect.effect-fadeIn.delay(playsinline)
                source(src="images/charts/IAS_17.mp4", type="video/mp4")
    .swiper-slide
      .content
        div.container
          .row.start-md
            .col-md-4
              h2.text-subtitle.text-blue.reveal.effect.effect-reveal Brands and agencies also differ on where they see 2018 opportunities.
              .strip.blue
              .spacer
              .text-body.effect.effect-reveal
                p.text-blue Brands are 16% more likely than agencies to see greater opportunity in cross-device advertising. However, agencies are 13% more likely than brands to see 2018 as a year of programmatic TV opportunity.
              .foot-note.blue.effect.effect-fadeIn
                img.foot-note__icon(src="images/question-red.svg")
                p.text-blue In your opinion, which of the following will offer A GREATER opportunity for advertisers in 2018 compared to 2017? (Please select all that apply).
