              .spacer
              .text-body.effect.effect-reveal
                p.text-blue The industry, especially brands and agencies, has its eye on technologies that can automate big data processes like machine learning and AI. Publishers are more likely to see impact on the industry from AR/VR solutions and facial recognition technology.
